1
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:40,760
What?

2
00:00:41,400 --> 00:00:41,920
He is in

3
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:43,320
your room?

4
00:00:44,120 --> 00:00:44,720
No.

5
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:45,410
He...

6
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:46,040
I...

7
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:47,140
I...

8
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:47,610
Oh my.

9
00:00:47,680 --> 00:00:48,640
No.

10
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:52,640
There's no way I can clear my name now.

11
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:55,240
What an unfriendly world.

12
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:57,080
Oh, Yiyi.

13
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:58,880
Since you left,

14
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,920
I've had such a hard time.

15
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:01,560
Bad news!

16
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:02,940
Bad news, Brother Wei.

17
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:04,760
Bad news!

18
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:05,690
Brother Wei.

19
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:06,520
Sister.

20
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:07,800
You came just in time.

21
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:09,920
A great Nether Demon appeared at the foot of Mount Yaoting

22
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:11,840
and has taken control of a village.

23
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,720
They say the villagers

24
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:14,050
are all trapped inside.

25
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:15,000
Wei,

26
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,780
when are we going to save them?

27
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,480
The new node is here.

28
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:20,760
Just to be safe,

29
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:21,920
let's introduce ourselves first.

30
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,780
Little sister,

31
00:01:23,039 --> 00:01:23,880
who are you?

32
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:26,560
Lu Danyu.

33
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:27,539
Don't touch me.

34
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,200
What trick are you pulling now?

35
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:29,800
This time.

36
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:31,880
Is this another first-meeting act?

37
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:33,479
See.

38
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:36,440
This is also an old acquaintance who was poisoned.

39
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,000
Shishi,

40
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,240
where did you hear

41
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,440
this news from?

42
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,320
Brother Wei,

43
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:44,400
when I just passed by the mountain village over there,

44
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,759
I heard it from a cultivator who escaped.

45
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,800
I know I am not capable enough,

46
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,860
so I hurried to find you, Brother Wei.

47
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,000
Brother Wei, you are so powerful.

48
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,930
You can definitely capture that Great Nether Demon.

49
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:09,160
Could this kid like the male lead?

50
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,240
No way.

51
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,720
The male lead belongs to the female lead.

52
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,650
I must stop this.

53
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,160
Shishi.

54
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:14,160
Shishi.

55
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,420
You did a great job.

56
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:18,130
Let's go vanquish demons together right now.

57
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,440
Lu Danyu,

58
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,420
don't touch me.

59
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:22,120
You want to vanquish demons?

60
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:25,250
You can't even beat the lowest-level Underworld Demon.

61
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:26,800
Shishi,

62
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:29,320
how can you say that about Danyu?

63
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:31,280
Although Danyu's cultivation is not top-tier,

64
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,079
she still

65
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,770
honed it with great effort.

66
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:35,520
How can you be so contemptuous?

67
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,200
Brother Wei.

68
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:38,060
You're scolding me for her again.

69
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,560
Shishi.

70
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:49,320
Wu...

71
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,040
Brother Wei isn't yelling at you.

72
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,840
He's doing this for your own good.

73
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,840
He just doesn't want us to argue.

74
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:56,800
He's afraid you'll get hurt.

75
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,200
So he sounded a bit harsh.

76
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,680
How could you let down his good intentions?

77
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,160
Let's go.

78
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,600
Eliminating demons is what matters.

79
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,000
Right.

80
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,100
Eliminating demons is what matters.

81
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:16,260
Brother Li,

82
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,720
I'm afraid we'll have to trouble you

83
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,680
to come with us.

84
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,079
To eliminate demons alongside Lady Mu

85
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:23,040
is my honor.

86
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:24,160
I

87
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,060
am duty-bound.

88
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,680
My God.

89
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,800
I also have to guard against the two behind me.

90
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,480
Why am I so busy?

91
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,800
Oh, Yiyi.

92
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:37,280
Do you know how hard I work to maintain the stability of the world?

93
00:03:42,760 --> 00:03:43,960
Excuse me, young man.

94
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:44,880
May I ask,

95
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:45,800
did a nether demon

96
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,130
appear in your village?

97
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,480
How is that possible?

98
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,440
We are protected by the Mountain God here.

99
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,900
How could there be demons?

100
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:58,800
I...

101
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,720
That is what the person said.

102
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:02,600
What?

103
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,400
You don't believe it?

104
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:07,530
If not, follow me into the village to see for yourselves.

105
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,240
Let's go into the village first.

106
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,280
If there is a problem,

107
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,640
it will naturally reveal itself.

108
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:11,970
Yeah.

109
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:12,810
Xiaoxue,

110
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,640
you are right.

111
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,890
Something is wrong.

112
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:50,360
They are so poor,

113
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,010
yet they eat so well.

114
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,840
There is definitely a problem.

115
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,440
Look.

116
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:55,520
That cultivator

117
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:56,960
didn't lie to us after all.

118
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:57,680
Of course.

119
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,600
Brother Wei is so observant.

120
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,000
This village is quite big.

121
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:04,600
How about

122
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,760
we split up first

123
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,200
to gather information individually,

124
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:07,920
then regroup

125
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,780
and make a plan.

126
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:10,690
Xiaoxue,

127
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:11,520
that makes sense.

128
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:13,360
My daughter.

129
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,840
I don't want you to go.

130
00:05:16,200 --> 00:05:18,800
My poor daughter.

131
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:22,760
I don't want you to marry the Mountain God.

132
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,210
Is there really a mountain god?

133
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,280
Ma'am,

134
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,400
is your daughter

135
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,880
marrying the mountain god?

136
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:34,320
Yes,

137
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,240
young man.

138
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,040
Lord Mountain God,

139
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,320
every month,

140
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:40,159
he marries a new bride.

141
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:41,320
Only then

142
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:43,240
will he give us food.

143
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,760
This month,

144
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:47,159
it's my daughter's turn.

145
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:50,760
Although marrying a god means

146
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:53,080
no worries about food and clothing,

147
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,080
but...

148
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:59,600
I've never seen anyone come back to visit.

149
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:00,920
I'm afraid.

150
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,240
I can't bear to let her go.

151
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:06,320
My poor daughter,

152
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:08,440
why is your fate so bitter?

153
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:08,960
Ma'am,

154
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,280
if you don't want to marry your daughter off,

155
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:12,140
we can help you.

156
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,240
You?

157
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:16,440
Yes.

158
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:17,760
We

159
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,060
are willing to marry him in her place.

160
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:20,840
Really?

161
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:21,840
Really.

162
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,680
We admire gods too.

163
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:24,960
Then,

164
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,520
let me see.

165
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,480
Lord Mountain God likes...

166
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,080
He likes this kind.

167
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,200
Mhm.

168
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:45,960
Ah.

169
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,960
Thank you

170
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,720
for marrying the Mountain God in my daughter's place.

171
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,520
These are

172
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:58,360
special dishes unique to our village.

173
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,640
Please eat more.

174
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,460
No need to thank us.

175
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,940
It's the least we could do.

176
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,000
There's something wrong with the food.

177
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,860
I was careless.

178
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,240
Since you want to die so badly,

179
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,200
I'll grant your wish.

180
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,320
They are all gone.

181
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,780
Hurry up and look for them.

182
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:36,600
Xiaoxue,

183
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,200
Danyu,

184
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,280
Shishi!

185
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,600
Who?
